title: Bubble Guppies Season 1 Soundtrack
description:
I couldn't find a Bubble Guppies soundtrack anywhere else, so I extracted all the songs from the video files I had into MP3 format.  I figure there are people like me that are looking for these songs, so I've uploaded these MP3 files for all the kids to enjoy.

I'll be uploading the Season 2 songs soon, once I finish them.

This is my first torrent upload; please seed so that everybody can enjoy it!
